    "Encapsulating domain knowledge: The questions asked to select a suitable metric are mostly similar regardless of image modality or application: Are the classes balanced?",
    "Is there a specific preference for the positive or negative class?",
    "What is the accuracy of the reference annotation?",
    "Is the structure boundary or volume of relevance for the target application?",
    "Importantly, while answering these questions requires domain expertise, the consequences in terms of metric selection can largely be regarded as domain independent."
